wasmtime-publish opened PR #4929 from ci/release-date-for-1.0.0 to main:

This is an [automated pull request][process] from CI which is updating
the release date of Wasmtime 1.0.0 to today. This PR's base branch
is main and a second PR will be coming to perform the actual
release which will be targeted at release-1.0.0.

[process]: https://docs.wasmtime.dev/contributing-release-process.html
